These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: chinese, japanese, argentine, indonesian
1. Nationality:japanese is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:indonesian is between Nationality:chinese and Nationality:japanese##2
3. Nationality:indonesian is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | chinese | indonesian | japanese | argentine |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pear, tomato, peach, cabbage
1. Food:pear is on the left of Food:cabbage##1
2. Food:tomato is in an odd position##4
3. Food:tomato is on the left or right of Food:pear##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pear | cabbage | peach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: scientific, thriller, western, sports
1. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:scientific##3
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is between Movie-Genre:sports and Movie-Genre:thriller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | sports | western | thriller |

 #################################
 
