.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: raspberry, kale, corn, cherry
1. Food:kale == Food:kale##1
2. Food:cherry is on the left or right of Food:corn##3
3. Food:corn is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:raspberry is in an even position##4
5. Food:cherry is on the left of Food:kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | corn | cherry | kale | raspberry |

